      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"hope\" stuff feels so hollow though. Like you're just telling a dead person to try harder at being alive. It’s not just being lost... it’s like the substance of who I was is actually gone. There’s nothing left to find. Just this heavy, empty shell that keeps breathing because it doesn't know how to stop. It feels more like a burden than a life at this point.",
